FBIS3-39503 "drweu033_h_94011" FBIS-WEU-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 GERMANY Mercedes-Benz Workers `Temporarily' On Strike AU1702110094 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network in German 1000 GMT 17 Feb 94 AU1702110094 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Some 20,000 employees of the Mercedes-Benz works in Sindelfingen temporarily downed tools this morning. According to the IG Metall trade union, production came to a complete halt. The trade union also expects to hold warning strikes in other regions today. The employers' organization, Gesamtmetall, threatened lockouts in the event of regular strikes.
